<br>
You get exp for each flag, when you talk to a certain NPC. The exp is equal to one full AA point, and can be put into either normal exp or AA exp depending on your settings.<br>
<br>
If you get another flag later on you can still get a full AA point for that flag as well.<br>
<br>
To top that off you also get a charm, which improves with flags owned. (Including elemental flags and currently locked zones.)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub137.ezboard.com/feqtestregistryfrm14.showMessage?topicID=1451.topic" target="top">The charm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> is actually rather nice, and if you have a full set of flags you will gain almost 100hp/mana, 10 to all resists and a bunch to each stat. As well as some additional ac. Full set of flags means you can enter Plane of Time, not just the zones unlocked with this patch.<br>
<br>
And yes, the charm can be used by anyone, not only those with LoY. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solaneb>Solaneb</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://homepage.ntlworld.com/solaneb/pics/monk_solaneb.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 386<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/11/03 7:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4458.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flag reward</span><hr size=1> woot need PoS and BoT asap then :P <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=704687"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://homepage.ntlworld.com/solaneb/pics/iksar_solaneb.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
